# Quality Gate After Edits

After any code edit, the agent must run the full quality gate before finishing:

1. `npm run format:check`
2. `npm run typecheck`
3. `npm run lint`
4. `npm run test:ci`

If one of these fails, the agent must fix the issue and rerun the full sequence until all checks pass.

Do not finish the task while the quality gate is failing.
